languages.text: {n}Хейнрикс холодно хмыкает.{/n} "Не Вольному Торговцу перечить воле Лорд-инквизитора, благодаря которой я нахожусь в этой свите".
{n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."

languages.text: {n}Heinrix lacht kalt.{/n} "Es steht {mf|dem Freihändler|der Freihändlerin} nicht zu, dem Willen des Großinquisitors zu widersprechen. Ich bin auf sein Geheiß in dieser Entourage, nicht auf das Eure."
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."

traits.locale_text: {n}Heinrix nickt kalt.{/n} "Wenn dies die Entscheidung {mf|des Freihändlers|der Freihändlerin} ist."

languages.text: {n}Heinrix se burla, frío como el hielo.{/n} «No está en sus manos contradecir la voluntad del Lord Inquisidor, Comerciante Independiente. L{mf|o|a} acompaño por orden suya, no de usted».
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."

traits.locale_text: {n}Heinrix asiente con frialdad.{/n} «Acataré su decisión, Comerciante Independiente».

languages.text: {n}ハインリックスは冷ややかにうなずく。{/n}「自由開拓者がロード・インクィジターの意志に逆らうことはできません。我は御身の命令ではなく、ロード・インクィジターの命で御身の従者となっているのです」
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."

languages.text: {n}海因里希冷冰冰地哼了一声。{/n}“行商浪人无权忤逆大审判官的意愿。我之所以会与你同行，是出于他的指示，不是你的。”
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."

traits.locale_text: {n}海因里希冷冰冰地点了点头。{/n}“如果这就是行商浪人的决定，很好。”

languages.text: {n}Heinrix, soğukça dudak büküyor.{/n} "Hür Tacir, Lord Engizisyoncu'nun iradesine karşı gelemez. Ben senin değil, onun emriyle bu maiyette bulunuyorum."
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix scoffs coldly.{/n} "It is not for the Rogue Trader to gainsay the will of the Lord Inquisitor. I am in this retinue at his behest, not yours."
